00:01:45.740 --> 00:01:46.620
So good!

00:01:50.540 --> 00:01:51.900
Tomorrow is my birthday banquet.

00:01:53.660 --> 00:01:54.980
He'll be back.

00:02:31.780 --> 00:02:34.740
I pointed a gun
at Chen Shangfu yesterday.

00:02:35.500 --> 00:02:36.780
I froze.

00:02:38.260 --> 00:02:40.140
Couldn't even pull the trigger.

00:02:44.380 --> 00:02:45.900
Do you remember

00:02:46.420 --> 00:02:48.420
our first time shooting?

00:02:49.500 --> 00:02:51.100
I couldn't hit a single target.

00:02:51.580 --> 00:02:53.300
Wang Penghui once told me,

00:02:53.500 --> 00:02:54.980
"Good shooters are heartless."

00:02:56.260 --> 00:02:59.900
Only the cold-blooded shoot straight.

00:03:01.860 --> 00:03:03.340
Maybe he was right.

00:03:05.700 --> 00:03:07.300
But I only shot straight

00:03:08.340 --> 00:03:09.500
after meeting you.

00:03:13.580 --> 00:03:14.740
I want to protect you.

00:03:15.460 --> 00:03:16.500
I want to be strong

00:03:17.580 --> 00:03:18.940
to protect those around me.

00:03:25.860 --> 00:03:26.820
Let me fire the shot

00:03:29.060 --> 00:03:30.140
tomorrow.

00:03:33.660 --> 00:03:34.900
Let me be your gun.

00:03:36.620 --> 00:03:37.420
Okay?

00:03:49.340 --> 00:03:50.140
Marshal,

00:03:50.340 --> 00:03:51.580
long life

00:03:51.580 --> 00:03:52.420
and happiness!

00:03:54.100 --> 00:03:54.580
Marshal,

00:03:54.700 --> 00:03:56.500
a humble gift for you!

00:03:56.940 --> 00:03:58.140
Thank you! Thank you!

00:03:59.260 --> 00:04:01.700
Marshal, you opium trafficker!

00:04:01.740 --> 00:04:03.940
The witness is locked here!

00:04:06.260 --> 00:04:07.180
Miss Liu,

00:04:08.300 --> 00:04:09.660
no proof,

00:04:10.380 --> 00:04:12.220
just slander me?

00:04:13.420 --> 00:04:15.500
Aren't you being too arrogant?

00:04:18.260 --> 00:04:19.060
Marshal!

00:04:19.700 --> 00:04:21.500
The people deserve the truth!

00:04:21.780 --> 00:04:22.940
He's in the secret room.

00:04:23.860 --> 00:04:24.820
I heard it.

00:04:26.260 --> 00:04:27.140
A secret room?

00:04:27.500 --> 00:04:28.500
Where?

00:04:29.500 --> 00:04:31.820
You want to search my house

00:04:33.100 --> 00:04:35.340
on my birthday

00:04:35.820 --> 00:04:37.620
with no proof?

00:04:39.340 --> 00:04:40.500
Is this proper?

00:04:40.860 --> 00:04:42.180
It's perfectly proper.

00:04:44.540 --> 00:04:46.100
Marshal Chen?

00:04:48.260 --> 00:04:49.700
Fine.

00:04:51.820 --> 00:04:53.980
Miss Liu, you're quite charming,

00:04:54.540 --> 00:04:57.340
turning my son against me.

00:04:57.700 --> 00:04:59.460
I suppose

00:05:00.180 --> 00:05:01.980
I can't stop you today.

00:05:06.100 --> 00:05:07.340
Then do it, feel free.

00:05:07.820 --> 00:05:09.700
Alright! I know where it is!

00:05:11.500 --> 00:05:12.100
Check it out.

00:05:12.100 --> 00:05:12.900
Let's go.

00:05:15.900 --> 00:05:16.700
Well?

00:05:19.660 --> 00:05:20.980
Won't you even

00:05:20.980 --> 00:05:21.980
call me "Dad" now?

00:05:39.460 --> 00:05:40.340
Where is he?

00:05:40.740 --> 00:05:41.620
There's nothing here.

00:05:42.820 --> 00:05:44.820
Miss Liu, I don't know

00:05:46.220 --> 00:05:47.540
who you're seeking,

00:05:48.060 --> 00:05:49.700
