00:05:53.140 --> 00:05:54.780
Since Wang Penghui's case,

00:05:54.940 --> 00:05:58.020
I've been concerned about opium.

00:05:58.900 --> 00:06:00.580
I found this by chance.

00:06:01.860 --> 00:06:03.340
It's from ten years ago,

00:06:03.780 --> 00:06:05.700
