00:06:06.340 --> 00:06:07.420
Remember, Miss Liu?

00:06:07.420 --> 00:06:08.180
What did you say?

00:06:08.300 --> 00:06:09.940
Forget him, go for the witness!

00:06:10.060 --> 00:06:10.860
Go!

00:06:29.580 --> 00:06:30.460
No news

00:06:30.460 --> 00:06:31.380
from the city exits.

00:06:32.420 --> 00:06:33.540
Nothing from the docks either.

00:06:35.540 --> 00:06:36.020
Let's go.

00:06:36.180 --> 00:06:37.060
Wenbin.

00:06:41.540 --> 00:06:42.420
You and your dad...

00:06:46.780 --> 00:06:47.740
Will you hate me?

00:06:49.980 --> 00:06:50.700
Song City's roots

00:06:50.700 --> 00:06:52.220
