00:07:00.660 --> 00:07:01.860
You helped me make up my mind

00:07:01.860 --> 00:07:02.940
to do the right thing.

00:07:04.620 --> 00:07:05.700
Don't blame yourself.

00:07:13.700 --> 00:07:14.740
